    </svg>



    <div class="welcome-message" style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold; color: black; ">
        <p>If you don't find the email in your inbox, please wait a few moments or double-check the email address you entered.</p>
        <p>We are here to help if you need any further assistance.</p>


    </div>


</div>
